---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro"
import Container from "@/components/Container.astro"
import FooterDivider from "@/components/FooterDivider.astro"
---

<Layout title="Newsletter" description="Sign up to my once-in-a-while newsletter.">
  <Container>
    <h1 class="md:text-center text-3xl md:text-5xl font-hardwriting font-bold text-grey-800 leading-tight">
      Newsletter
    </h1>
    <div>
      <form class="space-y-8" action="https://sendy.minafi.com/subscribe" method="POST" accept-charset="utf-8">
        <input type="hidden" name="list" value="892UVTIMgB51H8qkY76305YU2A" />
        <input type="hidden" name="subform" value="yes" />
        <div class="hidden">
          <label>
            HP <input type="text" name="hp" id="hp" />
          </label>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-8 divide-y divide-gray-200 sm:space-y-5">
          <div class="space-y-6 sm:space-y-5 prose">
            <div>
              <p class="mt-1">
                This is a very unofficial, unprofessional newsletter. I'm not trying to start a business, there are no
                sponsors and I'm just out to have fun with others creating cool stuff online.
              </p>
              <p class="mt-1">Here's what you should expect by joining this newsletter:</p>
              <ul class="mt-2">
                <li>I'll email you once a month with any new posts & whatever I'm up to.</li>
                <li>I'll keep your email safe and secret, never sharing it with anyone.</li>
              </ul>
              <p>
                That's it! My own email is in this same database â€“ and you can believe I make sure it's safe. Behind
                the scenes it uses a{' '}
                <a href="https://wp.adamfortuna.com/sendy" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">
                  Sendy
                </a>{' '}
                server that I host myself. Your email won't be stored in any large email provider database (Mailchimp,
                ConvertKit, etc).
              </p>
              <p class="italic text-sm text-gray-700">
                Side note: I'm still setting this up, so you might not get emails for a few weeks until I can figure
                out how to wire up my RSS feed to send out emails. ðŸ˜…
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-4 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
              <div>
                <label for="name" class="form-label">
                  First name
                  <input type="text" name="name" id="name" auto-complete="given-name" class="form-text" />
                </label>
              </div>

              <div>
                <label for="email" class="form-label">
                  Email address
                  <input type="email" name="email" id="email" auto-complete="email" class="form-text" />
                </label>
              </div>

              <div>
                <span>
                  <button type="submit" class="button" aria-label="Subscribe">
                    <span>Subscribe</span>
                  </button>
                </span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </form>
    </div>
  </Container>
  <FooterDivider />
</Layout>